    <data key="d0">Verkara Scalable DNS Edge Network Analytics Pipeline</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W4QzOaKCX2Y</data>
    <data key="d2">Ingests 20 TB of compressed data per day (6.6M records/second) from global edge DNS resolvers, processes it through EC2 transformers/aggregators to S3, cataloging it with AWS Glue, and querying via Amazon Athena to isolate workload query performance.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
